rules.description: left-command + right_command + semicolon to delete_or_backspace
map command + delete to option + 0
left-command + semicolon to delete_or_backspace
left-command + shift + semicolon to delete_forward
right-command + spacebar to enter
Change caps_lock to left_control if pressed with other keys, change caps_lock to escape if pressed alone.
Press Command + \\ to trigger F6 + \\ in Warp
Map Command + Shift + F to F6 + Shift + F
Map Command + P to F6 + P
Map Command + - to F6 + -
Map Command + Shift + - to F6 + Shift + -
map command + shift + P to f6 + shift + P
map command + shift + M to f6 + shift + M
map command + . to f6 + .
map command + left arrow to option + 6
map command + right arrow to option + 7
map command + shift + left arrow to option + 8
map command + shift + right arrow to option + 9
map option + shift + left arrow to option + 1
map option + shift + right arrow to option + 2
Change right_command+hjkl to arrow keys
map command + a to option + 4
map command + / to f6 + /
map option + delete to option + 5
map command + s to f6 + s
map command + f to f6 + f
map command + shift + e to f6 + shift + e
map command + b to f6 + b
map command + d to f6 + d
map command + shift + l to f6 + l
map command + g to f6 + g
map command + 1 to f6 + 1
map command + 2 to f6 + 2
map command + 3 to f6 + 3
map command + 4 to f6 + 4
map command + w to f6 + w
map command + shift + b to f6 + shift + b
map command + shift + w to to f6 + shift + w
map command + 5 to f6 + 5
command + shift + t to f6 + shift + t
command + t to f6 + t
map shift + enter to option + 3
map command + [ to f6 + [
map command + ] to f6 + ]
